: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1149029&amp;amp;li=18195760&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=05192026203855&amp;amp;lctg=8b37da73-f2d1-4a1c-8a9f-cb9d10343de6&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=mobile&amp;amp;collapse_width=550" style="display: block !important; width: 100% !important;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;从美国到德国，气候怀疑论者纷纷利用最近的研究作为全球变暖风险被夸大的证据。今天的时事通讯深入探讨了&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/PoPGHQRoWXeo43BO1CNTRLh60c0_rztMt9yxDuoq0EUD7pKVmaWKfEHl3Hxh5Ga1qLoJViocKZI0v7qkEDPqmil6HU13mcW0i9OA0ZU_A-kSq7-YBZLIF-qYNnRuItr5fk2t_sttti-kjA2g7IODwNMP_mybrmV1GCZsn22NsP8hKBlH-sZXildrEOXzrxXJ4doxPGmBwMuTem4ze3oe47dQeMPXQqUg_2JXzGesK8C6FI8-a-vK5J7l0XgobXJjH05w0lbjiIkiiAizIpNfWjgwyc4luTg_AnCXtSJ3Q7jkaEIm1HYsH4M00Ww9vy4g1lmoqEdfRfmiT_WsIvvgsHHuBmYJzQR_4uEAAucCCHWWh-TEPdJdFZ5AkplyNQKoQNybuNOHiww13IO9a7HIaQEDLOeR_mSSijrLga0XZw7Nm_BX8iwFdCqBijyrD9E47wFTLx_AO44_4AW9y3CoS_mrQZee9bTWehEFattQSyfcAr5GfvIbPxXGFjEwYBITpJQW9Sqv0YeohiGlF-xsbNUkzfFDjQlTPEbxfqyTqBwXjoavzRf0jUwbZc97b1vL/4AJVFHi05_3ezw02BbSno87K9d7AYxCE/20" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="科学家们在特朗普的嘲笑下放弃了最坏的气候情景"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;关于 RCP8.5 的争论&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;，这是科学家现已排除的最坏情况预测。与此同时，彭博新能源财经的研究人员在今年的&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/PTU47jH9Bk_G8_-0076KsPfmjQGDWBrRhBI6NN_4BI9n3uhey9c6-xjmD-ez_lx8HUw9Yo6DyNav_xqiC71VHp6u9Ef4-OVrKlQfS8KyagAB6WGx-GOXpyQbAiwc8_xyav0xxRuV66zNJtSofkbDALeP0EI5XmUAjhgUgEmgwJz_doskK0-oSbvkzKePEqJw7v26JIOO7IklFtP0lVpZ4Hd0BJ_v8lVDW76Osc4PH_M55nIPlHxPlJ7LEVL8OmpaL-g7UuGNY5aMCTKtNVV1BPbBcG3s5Dy39M5CtahylF5BPLhBJSRzToWAoqg4WE2eEwNAoXG2K9Ank-YxqOUkXKyusGy9BLv5iPq2PUkRNBHQ0I_n2Z5FvglumKjjKEziukdlE70uzuam8fTbJ9sJ_Ah33Bn